    "Summary": "MCP server inside the s&box editor. Connect Claude Code, Cursor, Claude Desktop or VS Code and let AI drive scenes, assets, ModelDoc, AnimGraph, ShaderGraph, ActionGraph and more.",
    "Description": "Install this library, open the MCP dock (View → MCP), copy the config for your AI client — done. Exposes ~60 editor tools over the Model Context Protocol with a live activity feed, tool browser and permission modes.",
